a. the need to develop a public plaza and a tourism information center in order to gather people together and to attract more buyer;

b. create a market day every week for fisher folk and farmers;

c. encourage the vendors form the nearby barangays to sell all local products at the Public Market;

d. campaign for the promotions of all local vendors;

e. all local vendors are welcome to make a display at the Public Market, fish or meat section;

f. offer a three (3) months free of rent in the market; and

g. pass an effective ordinance prohibiting all vendors located along the road right of way for reason of high risk of vehicular accidents.
